{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Good afternoon, everybody."},{"time":2000,"text":"I've got something to show you."},{"time":22000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":24000,"text":"Think about this as a pixel, a flying pixel."},{"time":27000,"text":"This is what we call, in our lab, sensible design."},{"time":30000,"text":"Let me tell you a bit about it."},{"time":32000,"text":"Now if you take this picture -- I'm Italian originally,"},{"time":35000,"text":"and every boy in Italy grows up"},{"time":37000,"text":"with this picture on the wall of his bedroom --"},{"time":39000,"text":"but the reason I'm showing you this"},{"time":41000,"text":"is that something very interesting"},{"time":43000,"text":"happened in Formula 1 racing"},{"time":45000,"text":"over the past couple of decades."},{"time":47000,"text":"Now some time ago,"},{"time":49000,"text":"if you wanted to win a Formula 1 race,"},{"time":51000,"text":"you take a budget, and you bet your budget"},{"time":53000,"text":"on a good driver and a good car."},{"time":56000,"text":"And if the car and the driver were good enough, then you'd win the race."},{"time":59000,"text":"Now today, if you want to win the race,"},{"time":61000,"text":"actually you need also something like this --"},{"time":64000,"text":"something that monitors the car in real time,"},{"time":67000,"text":"has a few thousand sensors"},{"time":69000,"text":"collecting information from the car,"},{"time":71000,"text":"transmitting this information into the system,"},{"time":74000,"text":"and then processing it"},{"time":76000,"text":"and using it in order to go back to the car with decisions"},{"time":79000,"text":"and changing things in real time"},{"time":81000,"text":"as information is collected."},{"time":83000,"text":"This is what, in engineering terms,"},{"time":85000,"text":"you would call a real time control system."},{"time":88000,"text":"And basically, it's a system made of two components --"},{"time":91000,"text":"a sensing and an actuating component."}]},{"cues":[{"time":93000,"text":"What is interesting today"},{"time":95000,"text":"is that real time control systems"},{"time":97000,"text":"are starting to enter into our lives."},{"time":100000,"text":"Our cities, over the past few years,"},{"time":103000,"text":"just have been blanketed"},{"time":105000,"text":"with networks, electronics."},{"time":107000,"text":"They're becoming like computers in open air."},{"time":109000,"text":"And, as computers in open air,"},{"time":111000,"text":"they're starting to respond in a different way"},{"time":113000,"text":"to be able to be sensed and to be actuated."},{"time":116000,"text":"If we fix cities, actually it's a big deal."},{"time":118000,"text":"Just as an aside, I wanted to mention,"},{"time":120000,"text":"cities are only two percent of the Earth's crust,"},{"time":124000,"text":"but they are 50 percent of the world's population."},{"time":127000,"text":"They are 75 percent of the energy consumption --"},{"time":130000,"text":"up to 80 percent of CO2 emissions."},{"time":133000,"text":"So if we're able to do something with cities, that's a big deal."},{"time":136000,"text":"Beyond cities,"},{"time":138000,"text":"all of this sensing and actuating"},{"time":141000,"text":"is entering our everyday objects."}]},{"cues":[{"time":143000,"text":"That's from an exhibition that"},{"time":145000,"text":"Paola Antonelli is organizing"},{"time":147000,"text":"at MoMA later this year, during the summer."},{"time":149000,"text":"It's called \"Talk to Me.\""},{"time":151000,"text":"Well our objects, our environment"},{"time":153000,"text":"is starting to talk back to us."},{"time":155000,"text":"In a certain sense, it's almost as if every atom out there"},{"time":158000,"text":"were becoming both a sensor and an actuator."},{"time":161000,"text":"And that is radically changing the interaction we have as humans"},{"time":164000,"text":"with the environment out there."},{"time":166000,"text":"In a certain sense,"},{"time":168000,"text":"it's almost as if the old dream of Michelangelo ..."},{"time":171000,"text":"you know, when Michelangelo sculpted the Moses,"},{"time":173000,"text":"at the end it said that he took the hammer, threw it at the Moses --"},{"time":176000,"text":"actually you can still see a small chip underneath --"},{"time":179000,"text":"and said, shouted,"},{"time":181000,"text":"\"Perch√© non parli? Why don't you talk?\""},{"time":183000,"text":"Well today, for the first time,"},{"time":185000,"text":"our environment is starting to talk back to us."},{"time":188000,"text":"And I'll show just a few examples --"},{"time":190000,"text":"again, with this idea of sensing our environment and actuating it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":193000,"text":"Let's starting with sensing."},{"time":196000,"text":"Well, the first project I wanted to share with you"},{"time":198000,"text":"is actually one of the first projects by our lab."},{"time":201000,"text":"It was four and a half years ago in Italy."},{"time":204000,"text":"And what we did there"},{"time":206000,"text":"was actually use a new type of network at the time"},{"time":208000,"text":"that had been deployed all across the world --"},{"time":210000,"text":"that's a cellphone network --"},{"time":212000,"text":"and use anonymous and aggregated information from that network,"},{"time":214000,"text":"that's collected anyway by the operator,"},{"time":216000,"text":"in order to understand"},{"time":218000,"text":"how the city works."},{"time":220000,"text":"The summer was a lucky summer -- 2006."},{"time":223000,"text":"It's when Italy won the soccer World Cup."},{"time":226000,"text":"Some of you might remember, it was Italy and France playing,"},{"time":229000,"text":"and then Zidane at the end, the headbutt."},{"time":231000,"text":"And anyway, Italy won at the end."}]},{"cues":[{"time":233000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":235000,"text":"Now look at what happened that day"},{"time":237000,"text":"just by monitoring activity"},{"time":239000,"text":"happening on the network."},{"time":241000,"text":"Here you see the city."},{"time":243000,"text":"You see the Colosseum in the middle,"},{"time":246000,"text":"the river Tiber."},{"time":249000,"text":"It's morning, before the match."},{"time":251000,"text":"You see the timeline on the top."},{"time":253000,"text":"Early afternoon,"},{"time":255000,"text":"people here and there,"},{"time":257000,"text":"making calls and moving."},{"time":259000,"text":"The match begins -- silence."},{"time":262000,"text":"France scores. Italy scores."},{"time":265000,"text":"Halftime, people make a quick call and go to the bathroom."},{"time":269000,"text":"Second half. End of normal time."},{"time":271000,"text":"First overtime, second."},{"time":273000,"text":"Zidane, the headbutt in a moment."},{"time":276000,"text":"Italy wins. Yeah."},{"time":278000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":280000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":283000,"text":"Well, that night, everybody went to celebrate in the center."},{"time":285000,"text":"You saw the big peak."},{"time":287000,"text":"The following day, again everybody went to the center"},{"time":289000,"text":"to meet the winning team"},{"time":292000,"text":"and the prime minister at the time."},{"time":294000,"text":"And then everybody moved down."},{"time":296000,"text":"You see the image of the place called Circo Massimo,"},{"time":298000,"text":"where, since Roman times, people go to celebrate,"},{"time":301000,"text":"to have a big party, and you see the peak at the end of the day."},{"time":304000,"text":"Well, that's just one example of how we can sense the city today"},{"time":306000,"text":"in a way that we couldn't have done"},{"time":308000,"text":"just a few years ago."}]},{"cues":[{"time":310000,"text":"Another quick example about sensing:"},{"time":312000,"text":"it's not about people,"},{"time":314000,"text":"but about things we use and consume."},{"time":316000,"text":"Well today, we know everything"},{"time":318000,"text":"about where our objects come from."},{"time":321000,"text":"This is a map that shows you"},{"time":323000,"text":"all the chips that form a Mac computer, how they came together."},{"time":326000,"text":"But we know very little about where things go."},{"time":329000,"text":"So in this project,"},{"time":331000,"text":"we actually developed some small tags"},{"time":333000,"text":"to track trash as it moves through the system."},{"time":336000,"text":"So we actually started with a number of volunteers"},{"time":339000,"text":"who helped us in Seattle,"},{"time":341000,"text":"just over a year ago,"},{"time":343000,"text":"to tag what they were throwing away --"},{"time":346000,"text":"different types of things, as you can see here --"},{"time":349000,"text":"things they would throw away anyway."},{"time":351000,"text":"Then we put a little chip, little tag,"},{"time":353000,"text":"onto the trash"},{"time":355000,"text":"and then started following it."},{"time":357000,"text":"Here are the results we just obtained."}]},{"cues":[{"time":360000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":363000,"text":"From Seattle ..."},{"time":371000,"text":"after one week."},{"time":398000,"text":"With this information we realized"},{"time":400000,"text":"there's a lot of inefficiencies in the system."},{"time":402000,"text":"We can actually do the same thing with much less energy."},{"time":405000,"text":"This data was not available before."},{"time":407000,"text":"But there's a lot of wasted transportation and convoluted things happening."},{"time":410000,"text":"But the other thing is that we believe"},{"time":412000,"text":"that if we see every day"},{"time":414000,"text":"that the cup we're throwing away, it doesn't disappear,"},{"time":416000,"text":"it's still somewhere on the planet."},{"time":418000,"text":"And the plastic bottle we're throwing away every day still stays there."},{"time":421000,"text":"And if we show that to people,"},{"time":423000,"text":"then we can also promote some behavioral change."},{"time":425000,"text":"So that was the reason for the project."}]},{"cues":[{"time":427000,"text":"My colleague at MIT, Assaf Biderman,"},{"time":429000,"text":"he could tell you much more about sensing"},{"time":431000,"text":"and many other wonderful things we can do with sensing,"},{"time":433000,"text":"but I wanted to go to the second part we discussed at the beginning,"},{"time":436000,"text":"and that's actuating our environment."},{"time":438000,"text":"And the first project"},{"time":440000,"text":"is something we did a couple of years ago in Zaragoza, Spain."},{"time":443000,"text":"It started with a question by the mayor of the city,"},{"time":446000,"text":"who came to us saying"},{"time":448000,"text":"that Spain and Southern Europe have a beautiful tradition"},{"time":451000,"text":"of using water in public space, in architecture."},{"time":454000,"text":"And the question was: How could technology, new technology,"},{"time":456000,"text":"be added to that?"},{"time":458000,"text":"And one of the ideas that was developed at MIT in a workshop"},{"time":461000,"text":"was, imagine this pipe, and you've got valves,"},{"time":464000,"text":"solenoid valves, taps,"},{"time":466000,"text":"opening and closing."},{"time":468000,"text":"You create like a water curtain with pixels made of water."},{"time":471000,"text":"If those pixels fall,"},{"time":473000,"text":"you can write on it,"},{"time":475000,"text":"you can show patterns, images, text."},{"time":477000,"text":"And even you can approach it, and it will open up"},{"time":479000,"text":"to let you jump through,"},{"time":481000,"text":"as you see in this image."}]},{"cues":[{"time":483000,"text":"Well, we presented this to Mayor Belloch."},{"time":485000,"text":"He liked it very much."},{"time":487000,"text":"And we got a commission to design a building"},{"time":489000,"text":"at the entrance of the expo."},{"time":491000,"text":"We called it Digital Water Pavilion."},{"time":493000,"text":"The whole building is made of water."},{"time":498000,"text":"There's no doors or windows,"},{"time":500000,"text":"but when you approach it,"},{"time":502000,"text":"it will open up to let you in."},{"time":504000,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":517000,"text":"The roof also is covered with water."},{"time":522000,"text":"And if there's a bit of wind,"},{"time":524000,"text":"if you want to minimize splashing, you can actually lower the roof."},{"time":529000,"text":"Or you could close the building,"},{"time":531000,"text":"and the whole architecture will disappear,"},{"time":533000,"text":"like in this case."},{"time":535000,"text":"You know, these days, you always get images during the winter,"},{"time":537000,"text":"when they take the roof down,"},{"time":539000,"text":"of people who have been there and said, \"They demolished the building.\""},{"time":542000,"text":"No, they didn't demolish it, just when it goes down,"},{"time":544000,"text":"the architecture almost disappears."},{"time":546000,"text":"Here's the building working."},{"time":549000,"text":"You see the person puzzled about what was going on inside."},{"time":552000,"text":"And here was myself trying not to get wet,"},{"time":554000,"text":"testing the sensors that open the water."}]},{"cues":[{"time":557000,"text":"Well, I should tell you now what happened one night"},{"time":559000,"text":"when all of the sensors stopped working."},{"time":562000,"text":"But actually that night, it was even more fun."},{"time":565000,"text":"All the kids from Zaragoza came to the building,"},{"time":567000,"text":"because the way of engaging with the building became something different."},{"time":570000,"text":"Not anymore a building that would open up to let you in,"},{"time":573000,"text":"but a building that would still make cuts and holes through the water,"},{"time":576000,"text":"and you had to jump without getting wet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":578000,"text":"(Video) (Crowd Noise)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":591000,"text":"And that was, for us, was very interesting,"},{"time":593000,"text":"because, as architects, as engineers, as designers,"},{"time":596000,"text":"we always think about how people will use the things we design."},{"time":599000,"text":"But then reality's always unpredictable."},{"time":602000,"text":"And that's the beauty of doing things"},{"time":604000,"text":"that are used and interact with people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":606000,"text":"Here is an image then of the building"},{"time":608000,"text":"with the physical pixels, the pixels made of water,"},{"time":610000,"text":"and then projections on them."},{"time":613000,"text":"And this is what led us to think about"},{"time":615000,"text":"the following project I'll show you now."},{"time":617000,"text":"That's, imagine those pixels could actually start flying."},{"time":620000,"text":"Imagine you could have small helicopters"},{"time":622000,"text":"that move in the air,"},{"time":624000,"text":"and then each of them with a small pixel in changing lights --"},{"time":627000,"text":"almost as a cloud that can move in space."},{"time":630000,"text":"Here is the video."}]},{"cues":[{"time":632000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":638000,"text":"So imagine one helicopter,"},{"time":641000,"text":"like the one we saw before,"},{"time":646000,"text":"moving with others,"},{"time":649000,"text":"in synchrony."},{"time":651000,"text":"So you can have this cloud."},{"time":660000,"text":"You can have a kind of flexible screen or display, like this --"},{"time":664000,"text":"a regular configuration in two dimensions."},{"time":674000,"text":"Or in regular, but in three dimensions,"},{"time":677000,"text":"where the thing that changes is the light,"},{"time":679000,"text":"not the pixels' position."},{"time":691000,"text":"You can play with a different type."},{"time":693000,"text":"Imagine your screen could just appear"},{"time":695000,"text":"in different scales or sizes,"},{"time":698000,"text":"different types of resolution."},{"time":710000,"text":"But then the whole thing can be"},{"time":712000,"text":"just a 3D cloud of pixels"},{"time":714000,"text":"that you can approach and move through it"},{"time":717000,"text":"and see from many, many directions."},{"time":720000,"text":"Here is the real Flyfire"},{"time":722000,"text":"control and going down to form the regular grid as before."},{"time":726000,"text":"When you turn on the light, actually you see this. So the same as we saw before."},{"time":729000,"text":"And imagine each of them then controlled by people."},{"time":731000,"text":"You can have each pixel"},{"time":733000,"text":"having an input that comes from people,"},{"time":735000,"text":"from people's movement, or so and so."}]},{"cues":[{"time":737000,"text":"I want to show you something here for the first time."},{"time":740000,"text":"We've been working with Roberto Bolle,"},{"time":742000,"text":"one of today's top ballet dancers --"},{"time":744000,"text":"the √©toile at Metropolitan in New York"},{"time":746000,"text":"and La Scala in Milan --"},{"time":748000,"text":"and actually captured his movement in 3D"},{"time":750000,"text":"in order to use it as an input for Flyfire."},{"time":753000,"text":"And here you can see Roberto dancing."},{"time":758000,"text":"You see on the left the pixels,"},{"time":760000,"text":"the different resolutions being captured."},{"time":762000,"text":"It's both 3D scanning in real time"},{"time":764000,"text":"and motion capture."},{"time":768000,"text":"So you can reconstruct a whole movement."},{"time":775000,"text":"You can go all the way through."},{"time":781000,"text":"But then, once we have the pixels, then you can play with them"},{"time":783000,"text":"and play with color and movement"},{"time":786000,"text":"and gravity and rotation."},{"time":789000,"text":"So we want to use this as one of the possible inputs"},{"time":791000,"text":"for Flyfire."}]},{"cues":[{"time":812000,"text":"I wanted to show you the last project we are working on."},{"time":814000,"text":"It's something we're working on for the London Olympics."},{"time":816000,"text":"It's called The Cloud."},{"time":818000,"text":"And the idea here is, imagine, again,"},{"time":820000,"text":"we can involve people"},{"time":822000,"text":"in doing something and changing our environment --"},{"time":825000,"text":"almost to impart what we call cloud raising --"},{"time":827000,"text":"like barn raising, but with a cloud."},{"time":829000,"text":"Imagine you can have everybody make a small donation for one pixel."},{"time":833000,"text":"And I think what is remarkable"},{"time":835000,"text":"that has happened over the past couple of years"},{"time":837000,"text":"is that, over the past couple of decades,"},{"time":839000,"text":"we went from the physical world to the digital one."},{"time":842000,"text":"This has been digitizing everything, knowledge,"},{"time":844000,"text":"and making that accessible through the Internet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":846000,"text":"Now today, for the first time --"},{"time":848000,"text":"and the Obama campaign showed us this --"},{"time":850000,"text":"we can go from the digital world,"},{"time":852000,"text":"from the self-organizing power of networks,"},{"time":854000,"text":"to the physical one."},{"time":856000,"text":"This can be, in our case,"},{"time":858000,"text":"we want to use it for designing and doing a symbol."},{"time":860000,"text":"That means something built in a city."},{"time":862000,"text":"But tomorrow it can be,"},{"time":864000,"text":"in order to tackle today's pressing challenges --"},{"time":867000,"text":"think about climate change or CO2 emissions --"},{"time":869000,"text":"how we can go from the digital world to the physical one."},{"time":872000,"text":"So the idea that we can actually involve people"},{"time":874000,"text":"in doing this thing together, collectively."}]},{"cues":[{"time":876000,"text":"The cloud is a cloud, again, made of pixels,"},{"time":879000,"text":"in the same way as the real cloud"},{"time":881000,"text":"is a cloud made of particles."},{"time":883000,"text":"And those particles are water,"},{"time":885000,"text":"where our cloud is a cloud of pixels."},{"time":887000,"text":"It's a physical structure in London, but covered with pixels."},{"time":890000,"text":"You can move inside, have different types of experiences."},{"time":892000,"text":"You can actually see from underneath,"},{"time":894000,"text":"sharing the main moments"},{"time":896000,"text":"for the Olympics in 2012 and beyond,"},{"time":899000,"text":"and really using it as a way to connect with the community."},{"time":903000,"text":"So both the physical cloud in the sky"},{"time":907000,"text":"and something you can go to the top [of],"},{"time":910000,"text":"like London's new mountaintop."},{"time":912000,"text":"You can enter inside it."},{"time":914000,"text":"And a kind of new digital beacon for the night --"},{"time":917000,"text":"but most importantly,"},{"time":919000,"text":"a new type of experience for anybody who will go to the top."}]},{"cues":[{"time":922000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":924000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}